      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://grokipedia.com/page/Bay_Hill,_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Bay Hill sits on either side of Apopka‑Vineland Road, north of Lake Buena Vista and south of Windermere.",
